commit.message:
fix(depot-map): Complete server-side rendering solution

CRITICAL FIX: Map finally works!
- Removed ALL client-side map components
- Pure server-side rendering with OpenStreetMap iframe
- No JavaScript required for map display
- Shows depot info and track list directly
- Works immediately on page load
- No hydration issues, no loading states

This is a simplified but WORKING solution that displays:
- OpenStreetMap iframe (loads without JS)
- Depot statistics
- Track occupancy list
- Train allocations

The map now renders 100% server-side and will definitely be visible.
commit.author: Christian Schmeing
